rows.label: qev041906_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ah! Here comes worm, all ready to be smooshed by
mighty Jalolo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0002
rows.name:
Well, worm? What will it be? Pay back money,
or cut off hair? Or maybe worm will break contract
and choose exile from Nopon society?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0003
rows.name: Choose how Jalolo will be entertained today![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0004
rows.name:
Nio was unable to get the money.
Jalolo can have tuft.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0005
rows.name:
Meh! Then let Jalolo see you cut it off here and now.
Jalolo want to see beginning of humiliating life for
Nio as bald Nopon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0006
rows.name:
Popo will cut. Jalolo should watch close to see what
this foolish contract has earned.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0007
rows.name: Ready for Popo to begin, Nio?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0008
rows.name:
Nio would let beautiful Popo do anything.
No need to hold back![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0009
rows.name:
Meh heh heh heh! So shameful! Much humiliating!
Young miss can't possibly marry Nopon who look
like that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0010
rows.name:
Popo deserve wealthy Nopon with thick head of hair.
So why not marry Jalolo instead?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_JNK0010
rows.name: Get Angry

rows.label: qev041906_SEL0011
rows.name: Stand up to Jalolo's mockery.

rows.label: qev041906_JNK0020
rows.name: Watch

rows.label: qev041906_SEL0021
rows.name: Wait and see how the scene plays out.

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0011
rows.name:
Jalolo never sign contract forbidding laughter.
Besides, how does friend expect Jalolo NOT to laugh
at sight like this?! Meh heh heh heh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0012
rows.name: Thank you, friend. But Nio not mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0013
rows.name:
Nio have someone who love him even like this.
Others can laugh, so long as Nio has Popo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0014
rows.name:
Popo might consider it if Jalolo plucked out every last
shred of filthy, putrid personality![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0015
rows.name:
Popo happy to sign contract right now,
if Jalolo want...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0016
rows.name: Rgh! Such the loathsome pair...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0017
rows.name:
Hmph! Fine. Contract is complete.
Enjoy life of shame and ridicule, baldy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0018
rows.name:
And there he goes... Heh heh heh.
Ntoto think this plan is huge success.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0019
rows.name: Oh-hooo! Jalolo had no clue hair was fake.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0020
rows.name: Whew! Now we can finally have wedding.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0021
rows.name:
But...Nio still lost everything. Business will have to be
built back up from scratch. Is Popo really sure she
want this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0022
rows.name:
Oh, forget money! What Popo want is Nio. Though
shame Popo won't get to wear ring picked out by Nio.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041906_MSG0023
rows.name:
Nio so lucky. And Nio work reeeally hard to save up
money and buy another blue sparkly ring![ST:wait ]
